   Dakota, on Nov. 2, 2016. Emily Kask for NPR hide caption
   toggle caption
   Emily Kask for NPR

[204]Greenpeace faces a $300 million lawsuit after Dakota Access Pipeline
protests

   [205]February 24, 2025  The company behind the controversial Dakota
   Access Pipeline is suing Greenpeace for at least $300 million for
   damages the oil pipeline company says it suffered from protests in 2016
   and 2017.

